/p>\n<div class=\"rank-math-answer \">\n\n<p><strong>A.<\/strong> 5 to 6 persons can sit in a chopper for <a href=\"https:\/\/uttarakhandtrips.com\/char-dham-yatra-packages\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Char Dham Yatra<\/a>. It also depends on the total weight of chopper is not more than 420 to 450 Kg.<\/p>\n\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div id=\"faq-question-1703761843196\" class=\"rank-math-list-item\">\n<p class=\"rank-math-question \">Q. Is VIP darshan included in Char Dham helicopter packages?<\/p>\n<div class=\"rank-math-answer \">\n\n<p><strong>A.<\/strong> VIP darshan ticket counter facility is available only in <a href=\"https:\/\/en.wikipedia.org\/wiki\/Kedarnath_Temple\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Kedarnath <\/a>and Badrinath Dham. In Gangotri and Yamunotri Dham there are no special counters for VIP tickets however special pooja can be conducted through the temple&#8217;s priests.<\/p>\n\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div id=\"faq-question-1703761908892\" class=\"rank-math-list-item\">\n<p class=\"rank-math-question \">Q. Can we go Yamunotri temple directly by helicopter?<\/p>\n<div class=\"rank-math-answer \">\n\n<p><strong>A. <\/strong>No, The Helicopters land 6 kms away from Yamunotri temple, from there you will get pony\/palkis to Yamunotri temple.<\/p>\n\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div id=\"faq-question-1703763965872\" class=\"rank-math-list-item\">\n<p class=\"rank-math-question \">Q. <strong>What is the payment policy for Char Dham Yatra from Dehradun booking?<\/strong><\/p>\n<div class=\"rank-math-answer \">\n\n<p><strong>A.<\/strong> You need to deposit 50% of the advance token amount at the package booking time, and you can pay the rest 30 days before your Yatra.<\/p>\n\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div id=\"faq-question-1703764021267\" class=\"rank-math-list-item\">\n<p class=\"rank-math-question \">Q. <strong>What Services are offered during Char Dham Yatra by helicopter?<\/strong><\/p>\n<div class=\"rank-math-answer \">\n\n<p><strong>A.<\/strong> This 